@page "/"

<MudContainer>
    <MudGrid>
        <MudItem xs="12" md="8" >
            <MudCard style="height:100%">
                <MudCardHeader>
                    <CardHeaderContent>
                        <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" Color="Color.Primary">Kyle Welcomes You!</MudText>
                    </CardHeaderContent>
                </MudCardHeader>
                <MudCardContent>
                    <MudText>
                        I am currently a <Bolden>full stack software developer</Bolden> at File Dynamics Ltd. in <Bolden>Bristol, UK</Bolden>. The work is 
                        focused on building <Bolden>web</Bolden> and <Bolden>WPF</Bolden> applications, centred around the legal sector. I have a 
                        <Bolden>Master of Computing</Bolden> degree with First Class Honours. It was awarded at <Bolden>University of Central Lancashire</Bolden> 
                        in 2017, for the course <Bolden>Computer Games Development</Bolden>. I aim to eventually save up and get a doctorate, because 
                        who doesn't want to be a doctor of computers!?
                    </MudText>
                    <br />
                    <MudText>
                        I created this site as a place where I can dump my <Bolden>interests</Bolden> and <Bolden>memories</Bolden>, develop and show off some <Bolden>small projects</Bolden>,
                        and hopefully help others (and myself) to <Bolden>learn</Bolden>! It's also become a good excuse to develop something using the <Bolden>Blazor WASM with .NET 6</Bolden>
                        (making modern websites for the non-technical folk)! I hope you enjoy your visit - please don't hesitate to <Bolden>contact me</Bolden> if notice issues with the site; 
                        want to suggest improvements; or just to say hi! There's a contact quick-link at the top right.
                    </MudText>
                    <br />
                    <MudText>If you'd like to know more about me personally, please follow the link below (or see the <Bolden>About Me</Bolden> link in the navigation menu).</MudText>
                </MudCardContent>
                <MudCardActions>
                    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Info" Link="/aboutme">Learn  about Kyle</MudButton>
                </MudCardActions>
            </MudCard>
        </MudItem>

        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
            <MudCard style="height:100%">
                <MudCardMedia Image="./images/SFAS/SFAS W2017 Winners.jpg" Height="400" />
                <MudCardContent>
                    <MudText>
                        I won Search for a Star in 2017 with the <Bolden>Star Wrangler Arena</Bolden> project (I'm on the left).
                    </MudText>
                </MudCardContent>
                <MudCardActions>
                    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Info" Link="/sfas">Learn More</MudButton>
                </MudCardActions>
            </MudCard>
        </MudItem>
    
        <MudItem sm="12" md="6">
            <MudCard style="height:100%">
                <MudCardHeader>
                    <CardHeaderContent>
                        <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" Color="Color.Primary">Star Wrangler Arena</MudText>
                    </CardHeaderContent>
                </MudCardHeader>
                <MudCardMedia Image="./images/SFAS/SWA Ability.jpg" Height="400"/>
                <MudCardContent>
                    <MudText>
                        A single- or muilti-player game where you score points by directing stars into the goals using a ship with abilities.
                    </MudText>
                </MudCardContent>
                <MudCardActions>
                    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Info" Link="/projects/star-wrangler-arena">Learn More</MudButton>
                </MudCardActions>
            </MudCard>
        </MudItem>
    </MudGrid>
</MudContainer>